Interface Summary
ConstraintInterface interface for checking whether a given premise-vector is compatible with the conclusion rules
RegExpInferenceMap.PremiseCombinatorInterface  
RegExpInferenceMap.RecombinatorInterface interface that returns a new iterable of assertion vectors for a given vector of premise that have given forms
